reviews.review_text: Need Some Help .... This one needs a pitch correction from one of the "mastering wizards" out there .......

sounds pretty good to me i don't think this needs any pitch correctation Jerry's  voice sounds  about  where it should be and you know, the best  mastering is no mastering at all , if it don't  need it , don't fix it.  this source sounds much fuller than the other one i checked out that had no bottom at all.  anyway, there's  my two cents, that's  all i can afford. this sounds good  because it started in analog,  and there's  a good feel to the grooves,  what all the crap out there people are dancing to now, it sounds like machine muck, not the real deal musicating that this is offerating, thanks for all that...
